# Data files
# Raw dump is external (Kaggle/HF); train+val splits are regenerated by the
# corresponding cleaning notebook (deterministic, seed=42). Only test.parquet /
# test.jsonl are tracked — they pin the evaluation set for cross-model
# comparison per the evaluator agent spec.

# Bitext (dataset 1) — notebooks 01/02
data/raw/
data/processed/train.parquet
data/processed/val.parquet
data/instruction/train.jsonl
data/instruction/val.jsonl

# BANKING77 (dataset 2) — notebooks 07/08. test.parquet + test.jsonl tracked.
data/banking77/processed/train.parquet
data/banking77/processed/val.parquet
data/banking77/instruction/train.jsonl
data/banking77/instruction/val.jsonl

